The occurrence of (-)-mesembrane in nature is
somewhat unexpected in view of the biogenetic origin
of these alkaloids. All previous examples of alkaloids in
the mesembrine series have an oxygen function at C(6)
in keeping with the biosynthetic experiments 10 which
haveshown that theoctahydroindoleskeletonisderived
from the intact incorporation of tyrosine. Presumably
